Error codes
200-success
201-created
400-client bad request
401-unauthorized
403-authorized but access restricted (user trying to access admin routes)
409-conflict (username already exist)
429-rate limiting
500-internal server error

Routes

Theater Routes
    POST /theater
    Description:Adding new theater
    Body:
        {
            "name":"PVR INOX",
            "location":"Coimbatore"
        }

    GET /theater
    Description:Get all theaters (limit 20)
    Response:
        {
            "message": "success",
            "data": [
                {
                    "id": 1,
                    "name": "Alankar",
                    "location": "Ponnamaravathi"
                },
                {
                    "id": 3,
                    "name": "pvr inox",
                    "location": "peelamedu"
                }
            ]
        }

    GET /theater/location/polla
    Response:
        {
            "message": "success",
            "data": [
                {
                    "id": 4,
                    "name": "thangam cinemas",
                    "location": "pollachi"
                },
                {
                    "id": 7,
                    "name": "Rajan cinemas",
                    "location": "pollachi"
                }
            ]
        }
    
    
Movie Routes:
POST /movies
Request:
    {
    "name":"Mass",
    "duration":163,
    "language":"tamil",
    "genre":"Action",
    "cast":"surya",
    "rating":7.1
    }
Response:
    {
    "message": "Movie added successfully",
    "movieId": 9
    }

GET /movies?name=?
Response:                   //if name not provided
    {
    "message": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "id": 1,
            "name": "LEO",
            "language": "tamil",
            "rating": 8.1
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "name": "master",
            "language": "tamil",
            "rating": 8.3
        }
    ]}

