screen Routes:

POST /screen
Request:
    {
        "theaterId":1,
        "screenNo":1,
        "seats":100
    }
Response:
    {
        "message": "screen created successfully"
    }

GET screen?theaterId=3
Response:
    {
        "message": "success",
        "data":[
            {
                "id": 3,
                "screenNo": 1
            },
            {       
                "id": 4,
                "screenNo": 3
            }
        ]
    }

GET screen/3

Response:
    {
        "message": "success",
        "data": {       
            "id": 3,
            "screenNo": 1,
            "name": "master",   
            "language": "tamil"
        }
    }



Movie Routes
POST /movie - Add a new movie
GET /movie - Fetch all movies (limit 20) or search by name using ?name=value
GET /movie/:id - Get movie by ID
GET /movie/:id/shows - Get shows available for the movie (theaters, screens, shows)

Theater Routes
POST /theater - Add a theater
GET /theater - Get all theaters
GET /theater/location/:location - Search theaters by location
GET /theater/name/:name - Search theaters by name

Screen Routes
POST /screen - Add a screen
GET /screen?theaterId=value - Get screens by theater ID
GET /screen/:id - Get screen by ID

Show Routes
POST /show - Add a show
GET /show/:id - Get show by ID
GET /show?theaterId=value - Get shows by theater ID

Seat Routes
POST /seat - Add seats for a screen
GET /seat?screenId=value - Get seats by screen ID

General Routes
GET / - Health check, returns server status